data.description: Rare opportunity to own a beautiful home in Thurston County for a great price! Pride in ownership, the seller has made many upgrades - from a new deck to concrete curbing and beautiful exterior details, this house has been lovingly maintained with room for some easy, interior sweat equity. Only a 25 minute drive to Tumwater and just outside the darling town of Tenino, this house sits on a spacious, quiet, and level lot with plenty of parking space. 2 bedroom septic could mean room for growth (buyer to verify).
